title: Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
June 11, 2015

 



Presidential Nominations Sent to the Senate





	NOMINATIONS SENT TO THE SENATE:

	Brian R. Martinotti, of New Jersey, to be United States District Judge for the District of New Jersey, vice Stanley R. Chesler, retiring.

	Robert F. Rossiter, Jr., of Nebraska, to be United States District Judge for the District of Nebraska, vice Joseph F. Bataillon, retired.
